             was indicted for <rs id="t18130113-69-off398" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18130113-69-off398" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130113-69-off398" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18130113-69-cd399" type="crimeDate">7th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130113-69-off398 t18130113-69-cd399"></join>, two shawls, value 28 s. and one yard of crape, value 5 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18130113-69-victim660" type="victimName">
