                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130113-69-defend658 t18130113-69-punish403"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 38.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
